async function getNumber1(){return 10}async function getNumber2(){return 4}async function compute(){const t=await getNumber1(),e=await getNumber2();return t+e}const promiseToCompute=new Promise(t=>{t(compute())});promiseToCompute.then(t=>{const e=document.getElementById("result");return e.textContent=t,t}).then(t=>{const e=document.getElementById("result");e.textContent=e.textContent+" puis "+(t+2)});